    io.github.ericmedvet.jnb.buildable
     
    io.github.ericmedvet.jnb.core
    Contains two packages with classes, interfaces, enums, and annotations useful for obtaining and using builders (namely, Builder, DocumentedBuilder) and the NamedBuilder, which can be used for building objects based on maps (ParamMap and NamedParamMap acting as dictionaries) containing the data need for building them.
    io.github.ericmedvet.jnb.datastructure
    Contains a single package io.github.ericmedvet.jnb.datastructure which provides interfaces and classes for modeling a few data structures (e.g., Grid, Table) and useful concepts (e.g., NamedFunction, Parametrized).
